This paper discusses the use of service-oriented architecture and Web services in developing robotics applications and software integrated with the Internet and the Cloud. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also discusses the use of cloud infrastructures for robotics applications, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). Additionally, the paper discusses the design of robotics systems through the Web, which could place it in cs.SE (Software Engineering) or cs.CE (Computer Engineering). Finally, the paper discusses the integration of robotics systems with the cloud, which could also place it in cs.SY (Systems and Control).
